   |+---+                      |xxx||xx|
 R || 0 |    xx     /\  xxxx   +---+|xx|
 W |+---+           \/ x     x |xxx|+--+
 R || 0 |          Rst x     x +---+ +-+
 | |+---+              x     x |xxx|x|x|
 +->|PWR|              x     x +---+x|x|
   |+---+     xxx      x     x |xxx|x+-+
 +->|GND|+--+          x     x +---+   |
 | |+---+|U | ++ +----+x     x+--+--+  |
 G |O    |S | || | SD |x     x|xx|xx| O|
 N +-----|B |-||-|Card|-------+--+--+--+
 D       +--+ ++ +----+
                  ^  ^
                  SD Card
                  
1. Turn off Power to Main Controller
2. Insert SD Card
3. Turn on Power to Main Controller
4. Wait 1 Minute
5. Turn off Power to Main Controller
6. Remove SD Card
